{[%evp 0,40,19,-13,-13,-23,15,-9,3,3,0,19,4,18,15,11,11,19,19,15,15,21,21,30,
30,30,44,44,65,8,-16,55,58,58,167,129,167,179,179,147,179,156,238] In this
chapter, we will examine one of White' most important tries, 1.c4 e5. 2.g3 c6
